Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen and Catholicism, and the monks all lived in separate little huts, and there was a meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,center, and I used to come to the meditation center in the dark at 4 30 or 5 in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and you had the meditation center all to yourself, a kiva, a meditation kiva,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had it all. It was just a big circular building with a nice carpet, and I could meditate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for hours absolutely alone. It was wonderful. Zen Catholicism. They later moved on to Colorado
