Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,has never been known becomes instantly knowable why is that because in the infinite reality
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness in the beginning was the light in the beginning was the godhead
