Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to see as your consciousness advances
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to see as your consciousness advances
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to see as your consciousness advances
