Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality actualizes when conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the conditions, then, is your own state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you hold in mind then tends to actualize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind tends to actualize, yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind tends to actualize, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not based on causality, so you can't cause yourself to become rich, or cause yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to become famous, or cause yourself, and you see everybody out in the world trying to cause
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves to be successful, and .
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, the way to success is to be completely and totally the fulfillment of your own potential
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best degree that you can fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the best carpenter in town, to be the best shoemaker in town, to perfect whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,capacities you have, to be the best mother there is, the best father, to be an upright
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and responsible citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To be, to have good will towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To contextualize your life, all you need to do, you don't have to sit and meditate, you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to go um and om, you don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is have good will towards all of life and all of its expressions, no
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just give you the example, in previous lifetimes being beheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say to the headsman, listen, don't feel nervous, it's okay, it's only your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I always tell them, don't worry about it, it's only your job, and you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a good job of it, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So your last thought is good will towards the headsman, that he doesn't feel guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that he's fulfilling his obligation to the crown, he's fulfilling his obligation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to the crown, and therefore he's worthy of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So I respect the head, I always respect the headsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's another one of those heads-off lifetimes, which I haven't had in quite a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well let's start with the, we'll start with how we usually do this.
